# SpotAI Design System Rules

## Color Usage Rules

### ONLY use these color tokens from the SpotAI design system:

#### Primary Colors (SpotAI Brand)
- `primary` / `text-primary` / `bg-primary` / `border-primary` - #313a45
- `primary-hover` / `text-primary-hover` / `bg-primary-hover` - #6c7179
- `accent` / `text-accent` / `bg-accent` / `border-accent` - #5857e8
- `accent-hover` / `text-accent-hover` / `bg-accent-hover` - #8181ff
- `accent-light` / `text-accent-light` / `bg-accent-light` - #f5f5fe

#### Status Colors
- `success` / `text-success` / `bg-success` / `border-success` - #00b070
- `success-light` / `text-success-light` / `bg-success-light` - #e8fff7
- `warning` / `text-warning` / `bg-warning` / `border-warning` - #ff950a
- `warning-light` / `text-warning-light` / `bg-warning-light` - #ffe9cc

#### Gray Scale
- `gray-50` to `gray-900` - Use for text, borders, backgrounds
- `neutral-100` - #f5f5f5
- `zinc-200` - #e4e4e7

#### Color Palettes (Use sparingly, prefer primary colors)
- `teal-50` to `teal-900`
- `violet-50` to `violet-900`
- `blue-50` to `blue-900`
- `green-50` to `green-900`
- `yellow-50` to `yellow-900`
- `orange-50` to `orange-900`
- `red-50` to `red-900`

#### Utility Colors
- `white` / `bg-white` / `text-white` - #ffffff
- `transparent` / `bg-transparent` - transparent
- `black-50` - rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5)

### FORBIDDEN: Never use hardcoded hex colors like:
- `text-[#123456]`
- `bg-[#abcdef]`
- `border-[#fedcba]`

### FORBIDDEN: Never use arbitrary color values like:
- `text-red-500` (use design system red palette)
- `bg-blue-600` (use design system blue palette)

## Typography Rules

### ONLY use these font styles from the SpotAI design system:

#### Font Sizes
- `text-xs` - 12px, line-height: 100%
- `text-sm` - 14px, line-height: 20px
- `text-base` - 16px, line-height: 100%
- `text-lg` - 20px, line-height: 100%

#### Font Weights
- `font-normal` - 400
- `font-medium` - 500
- `font-semibold` - 600

#### Font Family
- `font-inter` - Inter, sans-serif (default)

#### Capitalization Rules
- `capitalize` - Use for labels, buttons, and navigation items
- `uppercase` - Use sparingly for emphasis only
- `lowercase` - Use for body text and descriptions
- `normal-case` - Use for default text styling

### FORBIDDEN: Never use arbitrary font sizes like:
- `text-[14px]`
- `text-[16px]`
- `leading-[20px]`

## Spacing Rules

### Use design system spacing tokens:
- `p-4`, `px-6`, `py-4`, etc.
- `m-4`, `mx-6`, `my-4`, etc.
- `gap-4`, `space-y-4`, etc.

## Border Radius Rules

### Use design system border radius:
- `rounded-sm` - 2px
- `rounded-lg` - 8px
- `rounded` - 4px (default)

## CSS Custom Properties

### Use CSS custom properties for dynamic theming:
- `var(--primary-color)`
- `var(--accent-color)`
- `var(--gray-200)`
- etc.

## Component Guidelines

### Always use design system components when available:
- `@spotai/design-system` components
- Import from `lib/spotai-design-system/components/`

### When creating custom components:
1. Use only design system color tokens
2. Use only design system typography tokens
3. Use only design system spacing tokens
4. Use only design system border radius tokens
5. Use proper capitalization rules for different text elements

### Capitalization Best Practices:
- **Labels & Navigation**: Use `capitalize` for menu items, tab labels, and button text
- **Body Text**: Use `normal-case` or `lowercase` for descriptions and paragraphs
- **Emphasis**: Use `uppercase` sparingly and only for strong emphasis
- **Consistency**: Maintain consistent capitalization within similar UI elements

## Examples

### ✅ CORRECT:
```tsx
<div className="bg-primary text-white p-4 rounded-lg">
  <h3 className="text-base font-medium text-accent capitalize">Title</h3>
  <p className="text-sm text-gray-600 normal-case">Description</p>
  <button className="text-sm font-medium text-accent capitalize">Edit</button>
</div>
```

### ❌ FORBIDDEN:
```tsx
<div className="bg-[#313a45] text-[#ffffff] p-[16px] rounded-[8px]">
  <h3 className="text-[16px] font-[500] text-[#5857e8] uppercase">Title</h3>
  <p className="text-[14px] text-[#6b7280]">Description</p>
  <button className="text-[14px] font-[500] text-[#5857e8] lowercase">Edit</button>
</div>
```

## Enforcement

- Always check the SpotAI design system at https://design.spotai.co/?path=/docs/lib-showcase--docs
- Use only the exact color tokens and typography tokens defined there
- Never use arbitrary values or hardcoded hex colors
- Prefer design system components over custom implementations 